title: Is that... ranked 3s I see?
body: TT is up and the only option there is ranked 3s. Will this be permanent or is this a one time thing?

replies.body:
Temporary.
They won't add more permanent queues until the server population grows enough.
Which would probably require improvement of internet services.
It happens all the time, is usually a bug. Abuse it while you can  ♥
